text: Jan-Peter Nikiferow (born 8 November 1971) is a German gymnast. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Magdeburg
